Please ensure that the project both builds and lints successfully and that all tests pass. Before building the project, linting, or running tests, be sure to in copy environment example file as follows:

```bash
yes | sudo npm install -g bun
cp app/.env.example app/.env
```

Always create tests to verify your implementation. Tests can be executed with the following statement:

```bash
cd app && bun install && CI=true bun test
```
